CommentBody:
Most likely the account used to run NEA does not have permissions to read the gMSA password.

Set-ADServiceAccount -Identity %GMSA% -DNSHostName %GMSA.DOMAIN% -PrincipalsAllowedToRetrieveManagedPassword %NEA SERVER%$, %ADMIN ACCOUNT%

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/StealthAUDIT_11.5/page/Content/StealthAUDIT/Chapters/03.Global_Settings/Custom_Credentials/gMSA_Configuration.htm
